title: Jenkins and Jonez - NFL Preview With The Gridiron Gals
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - NFL Preview With The Gridiron Gals
description:
The guys play body language detective to examine Russell Westbrook and Patrick Beverley’s interaction before being joined by The Gridiron Gals to preview the NFL season. Then they close the show recapping the latest episode of ‘House of the Dragon’. #Herd
